## Putting things in the parenthesis ()

When creating the function, we put a variable declaration inside the parentheses.

```dart
// We demand a String named 'playerName' to run this function!
void greet(String playerName) {
  print('Hello, $playerName');
}
```
Now the function won't work unless someone gives it a String!

